@startuml seq-realtime-merge
' Context: messaging
' Events: RealtimeReceived, DeliveryTickReceived
' SDD: PROM-REALTIME-OWNER-003–005, PROM-MESSAGE-STATUS
' Revision: 2026-07-19

title seq-realtime-merge — INSERT/UPDATE peer messages

participant "Supabase Realtime" as RT
participant "MessageService" as MS
participant "RealtimeAttachmentMachine" as RAM
participant "MessagingCoordinator" as Coord
participant "UI" as UI

Coord -> RAM : AttachRealtime
RAM -> MS : subscribe peer channel
MS -> RT : channel owner + peer filter

RT -> MS : PostgresChange INSERT|UPDATE
MS -> MS : filter peer relevance
MS -> MS : parse message\nrenderable or tick-only?

MS -> Coord : RealtimeReceived / DeliveryTickReceived
Coord -> Coord : merge message\n(preserve media on tick-only)
Coord --> UI : list updated

@enduml
